snippet.description:
A little thing I started on Thursday sometime after I watched this episode of Kitchen Nightmares. I just couldn't believe how they spiraled out of control. What did you guys think of the episode?
Today is their GRAND reopening! So if you live around Scottsdale be sure to swing by the place.
Sorry I haven't uploaded in a while! Hopefully this should tie you guys over while I keep working on the bigger animation projects! I've got my hands pretty full atm. Stay tuned! :)
